sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant SettingsUI as Settings Page + ProfileForm
    participant ProfileAPI as PATCH /api/profile
    participant SettingsAPI as PATCH /api/settings
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)

    Admin->>SettingsUI: Open /dashboard/settings
    SettingsUI->>ProfileAPI: GET /api/profile
    ProfileAPI->>DB: Read brand profile and related sections
    DB-->>ProfileAPI: Profile payload
    ProfileAPI-->>SettingsUI: Populate form tabs

    Admin->>SettingsUI: Save profile and contact updates
    SettingsUI->>ProfileAPI: PATCH profile fields
    ProfileAPI->>DB: Update BRAND_PROFILE and related tables
    DB-->>ProfileAPI: Updated profile
    ProfileAPI-->>SettingsUI: Success toast

    opt Update site-level options
        SettingsUI->>SettingsAPI: PATCH settings values
        SettingsAPI->>DB: Persist settings
        DB-->>SettingsAPI: Updated settings
        SettingsAPI-->>SettingsUI: Success
    end
